    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition and has been meticulously maintained to the highest standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep showroom shine, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts effortlessly, providing a driving experience that feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a collector-quality vehicle that requires absolutely no work.",
