    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for your next adventure with this wonderful vehicle! It has been well-maintained and is in good condition, offering a reliable and comfortable ride for its next owner. The interior is tidy, and it performs beautifully on the road\u2014a truly solid choice for anyone looking for quality and value!",
