    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, some minor dings, and the paint is starting to fade in high-sun areas. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear and there are some stains on the carpet. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, but it will likely need some suspension work and a tune-up in the near future to keep it in optimal shape. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind a bit of character and some upcoming maintenance tasks.",
