      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty ride and it\u2019s looking for a brand new home! This car has been so reliable for me and is still in really great shape, perfect for someone who wants a solid, comfy drive without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014I'm honestly going to miss it! Send me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin. I'm sure you'll fall in love with it just like I did!",
