    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8. This engine remains a masterpiece of atmospheric induction, utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings with treated shells and upgraded bolts, as well as new throttle actuators. The suspension geometry remains true, with the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) providing distinct damping profiles. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the kinematic integrity of the chassis and the thermal efficiency of the cooling system are excellent. This is a driver-spec example optimized for performance consistency.",
